# 🛠️ Asset Management System

A full-stack Asset Management System built with **Node.js**, **Express**, **Sequelize ORM**, and **PostgreSQL** for backend and database, using **Jade (Pug)** templating and **Bootstrap** for frontend.

## 📦 Features

- ✅ Company, Employee, Asset Category, Asset Masters
- 📋 Track Asset Issuing, Returning, Scrapping
- 🔄 Asset History (full lifecycle: issue → return → scrap)
- 📊 Branch-wise Stock View with total values
- 🔍 Filter by category, type, make, model
- 🔐 Simple secure backend

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

| Category    | Technology     |
|-------------|----------------|
| Backend     | Node.js, Express.js |
| ORM         | Sequelize       |
| Database    | PostgreSQL      |
| Frontend    | Pug (Jade), Bootstrap, DataTables.Net |
| Tools       | Sequelize CLI, Nodemon |

---

## 🏗️ Installation

git clone 
cd asset-management-system
npm install

# Create database
npx sequelize-cli db:create

# Run migrations
npx sequelize-cli db:migrate
npx sequelize-cli db:seed:all

# Run app
npm start
